      <title>HTML学习笔记</title>
      <link href="/2020/02/08/html-xue-xi-bi-ji/"/>
      <url>/2020/02/08/html-xue-xi-bi-ji/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p><strong>web标准的构成</strong>：主要包括结构、表现、行为<br>|标准|说明         |<br>—–|—–<br>|结构|结构用于对网页元素进行分类，现阶段主要是学html<br>|表现|表现用于设置网页元素格式、颜色、大小等外观样式、主要是CSS<br>|行为|行为是指网页模型的定义及交互的编写，现阶段主要学的是JavaScript</p><h3 id="HTML语法规范"><a href="#HTML语法规范" class="headerlink" title="HTML语法规范"></a>HTML语法规范</h3><p>和markdown语法有点类似，所有内容写在&lt;html&gt;&lt;/html&gt;这对标签内</p><p><strong>标签关系</strong>：包含关系和并列关系</p><pre class="line-numbers language-html"><code class="language-html"><span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;</span>head</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span>      <span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;</span>title</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span> <span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;/</span>title</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span>       <span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">&lt;!-- 包含关系 --></span><span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;</span>head</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span><span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre><pre class="line-numbers language-html"><code class="language-html"><span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;</span>head</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span> <span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;/</span>head</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span><span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;</span>body</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span> <span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;/</span>body</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span><span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">&lt;!-- 并列关系 --></span><span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre><p>|标签名|定义|说明|<br>—|—|—|—|<br>&lt;html&gt;&lt;/html&gt;|HTML标签|页面中最大的标签，我们称为根标签|<br>&lt;head&gt;&lt;/headl&gt;|文档的头部|注意在head标签中我们必须要设置的标签是title|<br>&lt;title&gt;&lt;/title&gt;|文档的标签|让页面有一个属于自己的网页标题|<br>&lt;body&gt;&lt;/body&gt;|文档的主体|元素包含文档的所有内容，页面内容 基本都是放到body里面</p><p>VSCode工具生成骨架标签新增代码:</p><pre class="line-numbers language-html"><code class="language-html"><span class="token doctype">&lt;!DOCTYPE html></span><span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;</span>html</span> <span class="token attr-name">lang</span><span class="token attr-value"><span class="token punctuation">=</span><span class="token punctuation">"</span>en<span class="token punctuation">"</span></span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span><span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;</span>head</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span>    <span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;</span>meta</span> <span class="token attr-name">charset</span><span class="token attr-value"><span class="token punctuation">=</span><span class="token punctuation">"</span>UTF-8<span class="token punctuation">"</span></span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span>    <span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;</span>meta</span> <span class="token attr-name">name</span><span class="token attr-value"><span class="token punctuation">=</span><span class="token punctuation">"</span>viewport<span class="token punctuation">"</span></span> <span class="token attr-name">content</span><span class="token attr-value"><span class="token punctuation">=</span><span class="token punctuation">"</span>width<span class="token punctuation">=</span>device-width, initial-scale<span class="token punctuation">=</span>1.0<span class="token punctuation">"</span></span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span>    <span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;</span>meta</span> <span class="token attr-name">http-equiv</span><span class="token attr-value"><span class="token punctuation">=</span><span class="token punctuation">"</span>X-UA-Compatible<span class="token punctuation">"</span></span> <span class="token attr-name">content</span><span class="token attr-value"><span class="token punctuation">=</span><span class="token punctuation">"</span>ie<span class="token punctuation">=</span>edge<span class="token punctuation">"</span></span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span>    <span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;</span>title</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span>Document<span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;/</span>title</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span><span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;/</span>head</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span><span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;</span>body</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span><span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;/</span>body</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span><span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;/</span>html</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span><span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre><ol><li>&lt;!DOCTYPE&gt;标签：文档类型声明，作用就是告诉浏览器使用哪种HTML版本来显示网页，这个声明位于文档中的最前位置，在&lt;html&gt;之前，它不是标签，只是声明</li><li>lang语言：用来定义当前文档显示的语言；en为英语，zh-CN定义语言为中文</li><li>charset字符集：字符集是多个字符的集合，以便计算机能够识别和存储各种文字。<code>&lt;meta charset=&quot;UTF-8&quot;/&gt;</code>,UTF-8也被称为玩过吗，基本包含了全世界所有国家需要使用的字符</li></ol><h3 id="HTML常用标签"><a href="#HTML常用标签" class="headerlink" title="HTML常用标签"></a>HTML常用标签</h3><p>标题标签<code>&lt;h1&gt;-&lt;h6&gt;</code></p><p><code>&lt;h1&gt;我是一个一级标签&lt;/h1&gt;</code></p><h4 id="段落和换行标签："><a href="#段落和换行标签：" class="headerlink" title="段落和换行标签："></a>段落和换行标签：</h4><p>段落标签在段落之间有间隙，会根据浏览器根据窗口大小调整<br><code>&lt;p&gt;我是一个段落标签&lt;/p&gt;</code><br><code>&lt;br /&gt;</code>换行，没有间隙</p><h4 id="文本格式化标签："><a href="#文本格式化标签：" class="headerlink" title="文本格式化标签："></a>文本格式化标签：</h4><p>粗体、斜体、下划线<br>|语义|标签<br>|—|—<br>|加粗|&lt;strong&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;或者&lt;b&gt;&lt;/b&gt;<br>|倾斜|&lt;em&gt;&lt;/em&gt;或者&lt;i&gt;&lt;/i&gt;<br>|删除线|&lt;del&gt;&lt;/del&gt;或者&lt;s&gt;&lt;/s&gt;<br>|下划线|&lt;ins&gt;&lt;/ins&gt;或者&lt;u&gt;&lt;/u&gt;</p><p>&lt;div&gt;和&lt;span&gt;是没有语义的，他们是一个盒子，用来装内容<br>特点：</p><ol><li>&lt;div&gt;标签用来布局，但是现在一行只能放一个&lt;div&gt;，大盒子</li><li>&lt;span&gt;标签用来布局，一行上可以放多个&lt;span&gt;，小盒子</li></ol><h4 id="图像标签"><a href="#图像标签" class="headerlink" title="图像标签"></a>图像标签</h4><pre class="line-numbers language-html"><code class="language-html"><span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;</span>img</span> <span class="token attr-name">src</span><span class="token attr-value"><span class="token punctuation">=</span><span class="token punctuation">"</span>图像URL<span class="token punctuation">"</span></span><span class="token punctuation">/></span></span><span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span></span></code></pre><table><thead><tr><th>属性</th><th>属性值</th><th>说明</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>src</td><td>图片路径</td><td>必须属性</td></tr><tr><td>alt</td><td>文本</td><td>替换文本，图像不能显示时，用该文字替换</td></tr><tr><td>title</td><td>文本</td><td>提示文本，鼠标放到图片上，显示的文字</td></tr><tr><td>width、height、border</td><td>像素</td><td>设置图像的宽、高、边框粗细</td></tr></tbody></table><p>相对路径：斜杠方向向左</p><ol><li>同一级路径：图像文件位于HTML文件同一级 如<code>&lt;img src=&quot;baidu.gif&quot; /&gt;</code></li><li>下一级路径：图像文件位于HTML下一级<code>&lt;img src=&quot;image/baidu.gif&quot; /&gt;</code></li><li>上一级路径：图像文件位于HTML上一级<code>&lt;img src=&quot;../baidu.gif&quot; /&gt;</code></li></ol><p>相对路径：斜杠方向向右，指目录下的绝对位置，直接到达目标位置，通常是从盘符开始的路径<br>例如：”D:\web\img\logo.gif”或者完整的网络地址”<a href="http://www.itcast/images/logo.gif&quot;" target="_blank" rel="noopener">http://www.itcast/images/logo.gif&quot;</a></p><h4 id="链接标签："><a href="#链接标签：" class="headerlink" title="链接标签："></a>链接标签：</h4><pre class="line-numbers language-html"><code class="language-html"><span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;</span>a</span> <span class="token attr-name">href</span><span class="token attr-value"><span class="token punctuation">=</span><span class="token punctuation">"</span>跳转目标<span class="token punctuation">"</span></span> <span class="token attr-name">target</span><span class="token attr-value"><span class="token punctuation">=</span><span class="token punctuation">"</span>目标窗口弹出方式<span class="token punctuation">"</span></span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span>文本图像<span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;/</span>a</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span><span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">&lt;!-- href 用于指定链接目标的URL地址，是必须属性 --></span><span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">&lt;!-- target指定打开方式，_self为默认值，_blank为新窗口打开 --></span><span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre><p>链接标签分类：</p><ol><li>如果是下载链接，地址链接的是.exe或者.zip等压缩包形式；</li><li>如果是内部链接，跳转目标是html文件名；</li><li>图片、视频、音频、文本都可以添加超链接,例如<code>&lt;a href=&quot;跳转目标&quot; target=&quot;目标窗口弹出方式&quot;&gt;&lt;ima src=&quot;img.jpg&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;</code>；</li><li><code>href=&quot;#&quot;</code>表示空链接</li><li>锚点链接：<ul><li>在链接文本的href属性中，设置属性值为<code>#名字</code>的形式，如<code>&lt;a href=&#39;#two</code>&gt;第二集`</li><li>找到目标位置标签，里面添加一个id属性=<code>名字</code>，如<code>&lt;h3 id=&quot;two&quot;&gt;第二集介绍&lt;/h3&gt;</code></li></ul></li></ol><h4 id="注释标签"><a href="#注释标签" class="headerlink" title="注释标签"></a>注释标签</h4><p>快捷键ctrl+/</p><pre class="line-numbers language-html"><code class="language-html"><span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">&lt;!-- 我想和手磨咖啡 --></span><span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span></span></code></pre><p>特殊字符:<img src="https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20200207142232544.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZmFuZ3poZW5naGVpdGk,shadow_10,text_aHR0cHM6Ly9ibG9nLmNzZG4ubmV0L3dlaXhpbl80MjgzODA2MQ==,size_16,color_FFFFFF,t_70" alt="在这里插入图片描述"></p><h4 id="表格标签："><a href="#表格标签：" class="headerlink" title="表格标签："></a>表格标签：</h4><pre class="line-numbers language-html"><code class="language-html"><span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;</span>table</span> <span class="token attr-name">align</span><span class="token attr-value"><span class="token punctuation">=</span><span class="token punctuation">"</span>center<span class="token punctuation">"</span></span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span>    <span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;</span>tr</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span>        <span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;</span>td</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span>单元格内文字<span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;/</span>td</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span>        ...    <span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;/</span>tr</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span>    ...<span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;/</span>table</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span><span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre><ol><li>&lt;tr&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;用于定义表格中的行，必须在&lt;table&gt;&lt;/table&gt;标签内</li><li>&lt;td&gt;&lt;/td&gt;用于定义表格中的单元格，必须在&lt;tr&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&gt;标签内</li><li>&lt;th&gt;&lt;/th&gt;表头单元格标签，表头会加粗居中</li></ol><p>表格属性：<br>|属性名|属性值|描述|<br>|—|—-|—|<br>|align|left,right,center|规定表格位置|<br>|border|1或””|规定表格单元是否有边框，默认””|<br>|cellpadding|像素值|规定单元边沿与其内容之间空白<br>|cellspacing|像素值|规定单元内容之间空白<br>|width|像素值或百分比|规定表格宽度|<br><strong>示例</strong> </p><pre class="line-numbers language-html"><code class="language-html"><span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;</span>table</span> <span class="token attr-name">cellspacing</span><span class="token attr-value"><span class="token punctuation">=</span><span class="token punctuation">"</span>0<span class="token punctuation">"</span></span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span>                <span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;</span>thead</span> <span class="token punctuation">></span></span>                    <span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;</span>tr</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span>                        <span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;</span>td</span> <span class="token attr-name">class</span><span class="token attr-value"><span class="token punctuation">=</span><span class="token punctuation">"</span>pl10 e1<span class="token punctuation">"</span></span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span>统计项<span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;/</span>td</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span>                        <span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;</span>td</span> <span class="token attr-name">class</span><span class="token attr-value"><span class="token punctuation">=</span><span class="token punctuation">"</span>e2<span class="token punctuation">"</span></span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span>沪市<span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;/</span>td</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span>                        <span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;</span>td</span> <span class="token attr-name">class</span><span class="token attr-value"><span class="token punctuation">=</span><span class="token punctuation">"</span>pr10 e3<span class="token punctuation">"</span></span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span>深市<span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;/</span>td</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span>                    <span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;/</span>tr</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span>                <span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;/</span>thead</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span>                <span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;</span>tbody</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span>                    <span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;</span>tr</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span>                        <span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;</span>td</span> <span class="token punctuation">></span></span>股票只数<span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;/</span>td</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span>                        <span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;</span>td</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span>{{= stat[0] }}<span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;/</span>td</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span>                        <span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;</span>td</span> <span class="token punctuation">></span></span>{{= stat[1] }}<span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;/</span>td</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span>                    <span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;/</span>tr</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span>                <span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;</span>tbody</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span><span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;/</span>table</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span><span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">&lt;!-- &lt;thead>&lt;/thead>包裹表头 --></span><span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">&lt;!-- &lt;tbody>&lt;/tbody>包裹表格内容 --></span><span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre><p><strong>合并单元格</strong>：</p><ul><li>跨行：<code>rowspan=“数字”</code>最上侧单元格为目标单元格，写合并代码</li><li>跨列：<code>colspan=&quot;数字&quot;</code>最左侧单元格为目标单元格，写合并代码</li><li>被合并的单元格的代码要删除</li></ul><h4 id="列表"><a href="#列表" class="headerlink" title="列表"></a>列表</h4><p><code>&lt;ul&gt;里面只能放&lt;li&gt;</code>标签表示html页面中项目的无序列表，一般会以项目符号呈现列表项，而列表项使用<code>&lt;li&gt;</code>标签定义<br><code>&lt;ol&gt;</code>标签表示html页面中项目的有序列表</p><pre class="line-numbers language-html"><code class="language-html"><span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;</span>ul</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span>    <span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;</span>li</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span>列表项1<span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;/</span>li</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span>    <span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;</span>li</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span>列表项1<span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;/</span>li</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span><span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;/</span>ul</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span><span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre><ol><li>&lt;ul&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;里面只能放&lt;li&gt;&lt;li&gt;，放其余标签是不允许的</li><li>&lt;li&gt;&lt;li&gt;相当于一个容器，允许容纳所有元素，除了文字还有图片等等都可以</li></ol><h5 id="自定义列表"><a href="#自定义列表" class="headerlink" title="自定义列表"></a>自定义列表</h5><p>&lt;dl&gt;标签用于定义描述列表，该标签会与&lt;dt&gt;(定义项目/名字)和&lt;dd&gt;(描述每一个项目/名字)一起使用</p><pre class="line-numbers language-html"><code class="language-html"><span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;</span>dl</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span>    <span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;</span>dt</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span>名词1<span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;/</span>dt</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span>    <span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;</span>dd</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span>名词1解释1<span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;/</span>dd</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span><span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;/</span>dl</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span><span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre><h4 id="表单标签"><a href="#表单标签" class="headerlink" title="表单标签"></a>表单标签</h4><p>一个表单通常由<strong>表单域、表单控件、提示信息</strong>3部分构成<br><code>&lt;form&gt;</code>标签用于定义表单域，它会把范围内的表单元素信息提交给服务器</p><pre class="line-numbers language-html"><code class="language-html"><span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;</span>form</span> <span class="token attr-name">action</span><span class="token attr-value"><span class="token punctuation">=</span><span class="token punctuation">"</span>url地址<span class="token punctuation">"</span></span> <span class="token attr-name">method</span><span class="token attr-value"><span class="token punctuation">=</span><span class="token punctuation">"</span>提交方式(get/post)<span class="token punctuation">"</span></span> <span class="token attr-name">name</span><span class="token attr-value"><span class="token punctuation">=</span><span class="token punctuation">"</span>表单域名称<span class="token punctuation">"</span></span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span><span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;/</span>form</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span><span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre><p><strong>表单控件</strong>：1.input输入表单元素;2.select下拉表单元素;3.textarea文本域元素</p><pre class="line-numbers language-html"><code class="language-html"><span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;</span>input</span> <span class="token attr-name">type</span><span class="token attr-value"><span class="token punctuation">=</span><span class="token punctuation">"</span>属性值<span class="token punctuation">"</span></span> <span class="token attr-name">name</span><span class="token attr-value"><span class="token punctuation">=</span><span class="token punctuation">"</span>表单元素名字<span class="token punctuation">"</span></span> <span class="token attr-name">value</span><span class="token attr-value"><span class="token punctuation">=</span><span class="token punctuation">"</span>框框中默认出现的内容<span class="token punctuation">"</span></span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span> <span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">&lt;!-- name是表单元素名字，要求单选按钮和复选框要有相同的name值 --></span><span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">&lt;!-- name和value是每个表单元素都有的属性值，主要供后台使用 --></span><span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre><p>&lt;lable&gt;标签为input元素定义标注<br>&lt;lable&gt;标签用于绑定一个表单元素，当点击&lt;lable&gt;标签内文本时，浏览器会自动将焦点(光标)转到或者选择对应的表单元素上，用来增加用户体验</p><pre class="line-numbers language-html"><code class="language-html"><span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;</span>lable</span> <span class="token attr-name">for</span><span class="token attr-value"><span class="token punctuation">=</span><span class="token punctuation">"</span>sex<span class="token punctuation">"</span></span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span>男<span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;/</span>lable</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span><span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;</span>input</span> <span class="token attr-name">type</span><span class="token attr-value"><span class="token punctuation">=</span><span class="token punctuation">"</span>radio<span class="token punctuation">"</span></span> <span class="token attr-name">name</span><span class="token attr-value"><span class="token punctuation">=</span><span class="token punctuation">"</span>sex<span class="token punctuation">"</span></span> <span class="token attr-name">id</span><span class="token attr-value"><span class="token punctuation">=</span><span class="token punctuation">"</span>sex<span class="token punctuation">"</span></span> <span class="token punctuation">/></span></span><span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">&lt;!-- &lt;lable>标签的for属性应当与相关元素的id属性相同 --></span><span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre><p>&lt;select&gt;标签用于多选元素</p><pre class="line-numbers language-html"><code class="language-html"><span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;</span>select</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span>    <span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;</span>option</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span>选项1<span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;/</span>option</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span>    <span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;</span>option</span> <span class="token attr-name">selected</span><span class="token attr-value"><span class="token punctuation">=</span><span class="token punctuation">"</span>selected<span class="token punctuation">"</span></span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span>选项2<span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;/</span>option</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span><span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;/</span>select</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span><span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">&lt;!-- 当&lt;option>中定义selected="selected"时，该选项为默认选项 --></span><span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre><p>&lt;textarea&gt;文本域</p><pre class="line-numbers language-html"><code class="language-html"><span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;</span>textarea</span> <span class="token attr-name">rows</span><span class="token attr-value"><span class="token punctuation">=</span><span class="token punctuation">"</span>3<span class="token punctuation">"</span></span> <span class="token attr-name">cols</span><span class="token attr-value"><span class="token punctuation">=</span><span class="token punctuation">"</span>20<span class="token punctuation">"</span></span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span>    文本内容<span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;/</span>textarea</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span><span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>]]></content>
      
      
      
